metadata.name: Dave Stewart
metadata.description: Dave Stewart live at The Hatfield Forum England when he was the lead guitarist of The Tourists. Asked to go to the venue to photograph the Yachts for their record company. I arrived early and the support band came on and they were incredible. Photo ©David Levine.
